a.n: One Day With Inessa, Saint Petersbourg

p.k: This new episode of One day with shares with you the private life of one of our new Playboy TV Europe models: Inessa Shein! Follow her daily life, from her morning routine with a relaxing bath to a hot photoshoot where she shows the beautiful body that she is very proud of. There’s still time for an intense fitness session and to shoot her TV show, in which she expresses all her passion about cars and speed… So don’t miss anything from her everyday life!
